reviewText: MI-5 is a great series that realistically shows the spy business and its tradecraft for what it really is....highly skilled individuals who seem quite ordinary, but accomplish great things under stress of the moment.  One of my favorite series of all times.
Slightly too violent for me, but it meets the fantasy requirement.  (Who could actually survive and have a successful career in MI5?)  Ros Myer is a super-heroine for me.
